    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334690/extras/1a94f0955a3f34dcb8c26445b9684a71.avif?t=1770379899\" width=616 height=354 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About the Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t just another case to solve. It’s a <strong>personal matter.</strong><br><br><br><strong>Please note:</strong> <i>Detective Malinowski</i> launches with <strong>Polish and English subtitles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polish voice acting is live, and <strong>English voice acting will be added soon</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some achievements—including the <strong>True Detective super achievement</strong>—will be added in a <strong>future achievement update</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sound as your guide</strong> – follow clues hidden in footsteps, creaking doors, and the melodies of an old radio.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Graphic compass</strong> – helps you navigate a world full of noise… and silence.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sketchbook album</strong> – each scene is an illustration in the book of your adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story and Achievements</strong> – there is only one ending. And only one <strong>True Detective Ultimate Achievement</strong>, which you earn by completing key achievements from all available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Noir atmosphere</strong> – original music and ambient sounds create tension. <strong><i>Headphones highly recommended.</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hear the footsteps? Don’t wait – the case is waiting.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
